title: Marvel NOW! Week 50 10/30/2013
description:
I didn't see a collected torrent for last this past week's Marvel NOW! titles, so I thought I'd upload one. Included are:

Avengers 022
Avengers A.I. 005
Captain America - Living Legend 02 (of 4)
Guardians of the Galaxy 008
Infinity 05 (of 6)
Punisher - The Trial of the Punisher 002 (of 2)
Scarlet Spider 023
Superior Spider-Man 020
Superior Spider-Man Team-Up Special 001
Uncanny X-Force 013

If you like them and have the money, buy them and support your favorite writers, artists, local comic shops and publishers. Thanks be to all the uploaders and scanners and seeders out there!
